ngesichts von political correctness, der me too-Bewegung und der Diskussion um fake news ist diese theoretische Reflexion des Wertens und Urteilens unerlässlich und hochaktuell.  afunded by Backlisttransformation EOSC Future  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aAllgemeine Literaturwissenschaft. 4aBeurteilung. 4aEthik. 4aFilm. 4aFotographie. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aKunst. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aNarratologie. 4aSlavistik. 4aUrteile. 4aVideospiele. 4aWerte. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aArt.  aAssessment.  aCultural Studies.  aEthics.  aFilm.  aJudge.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aNarratology.  aSlavic Studies.  aValues.  aVideo Games.1 aBurghardt, Anja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBurghardt, Anja, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEsin, Cigdem, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEsslinger, Detlef, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrimmel, Sandra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGallagher, Catherine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrob, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrübel, Rainer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHausbacher, Eva, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMurray, Soraya, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmid, Wolf, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aScholz, Nora, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1